snippet.title: Tiger versus Lion

snippet.title: HTC One M8 specs versus Samsung Galaxy S5, iPhone 5S
snippet.description: The new HTC One rustles up an impressive list of hardware features and a slick new software shell. So far, the 'M8' stands strong against its influential rivals.

snippet.description: One-off cars are always going to be fun -- especially when they're built in a shed in the east of England and can hit 62mph from rest in less than 3 seconds. It's also fun to put them on sand up against a Speedway rider. As you do.

snippet.title: Samsung Galaxy S5 camera shootout versus HTC One M8, iPhone 5S

snippet.description: The Surface Pro 2 starts at $899, but an optimal configuration will cost $1,129. What else will that investment buy?
